==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: White fly
<hw>White fly</hw>. <def>Any one of numerous small injurious hemipterous
insects of the genus <gen>Aleyrodes</gen>, allied to scale insects. They
are usually covered with a white or gray powder.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

